@startuml
title Vote Answer Sequence Diagram

actor User

participant VoteController
participant IVoteService
participant VoterServiceImpl
participant UserRepo
participant AnswerRepo
participant VoteRepo
database Database

User -> VoteController : Upvote/Downvote
VoteController -> IVoteService : vote(answerId,type)
IVoteService -> VoterServiceImpl : vote(answerId,type)

VoterServiceImpl -> UserRepo : findById(userId)
VoterServiceImpl -> AnswerRepo : findById(answerId)

VoterServiceImpl -> VoteRepo : save(vote)
VoteRepo -> Database : INSERT Vote

VoterServiceImpl -> AnswerRepo : updateVoteCount()
AnswerRepo -> Database : UPDATE Answer

VoterServiceImpl --> VoteController : Success
VoteController --> User : Vote Updated

@enduml